quran[399]{c,v,t}:
  51,31,(Aburahamu) aravuga ati “None ni iki kibagenza yemwe mwa ntumwa mwe?”
  51,32,Baravuga bati “Rwose twoherejwe ku bantu b’inkozi z’ibibi”
  51,33,Kugira ngo tubamanurireho amabuye y’ibumba (yacaniriwe)
  51,34,"(Ayo mabuye) yashyizweho ibimenyetso kwa Nyagasani wawe, akaba ari igihano ku barengera (imbago za Allah)"
  51,35,Nuko abemeramana (bari mu mudugudu w’inkozi z’ibibi) tuwubakuramo (kugira ngo ibihano bitabageraho)
  51,36,Ariko nta n’abo twasanzemo uretse inzu imwe y’Abayisilamu (urugo rw’Intumwa Loti)
  51,37,Nuko (nyuma yo kuwurimbura) tuwusigamo ikimenyetso ku batinya ibihano bibabaza
  51,38,"No mu nkuru ya Musa (harimo isomo), ubwo twamwoherezaga kwa Farawo tumuhaye ibimenyetso n’ububasha bigaragara"
  51,39,"Ariko Farawo yishingikirije ububasha yari afite, atera umugongo (yanga kwemera ubutumwa yari azaniwe), aravuga ati “Uyu ni umurozi cyangwa umusazi.”"
  51,40,Nuko tumufatana n’ingabo ze maze tubajugunya mu nyanja kandi agayitse (kubera ibikorwa bye by’ubuhakanyi)
  51,41,"No mu nkuru y’aba Adi (harimo isomo), ubwo twabohererezaga umuyaga ugumbahaye (udafite icyiza na kimwe, usenya nta cyo usize)"
  51,42,Nta cyo wasigaga mu byo wahuraga na byo utakigize umuyonga
  51,43,No mu nkuru y’aba Thamudu (harimo isomo) ubwo babwirwaga bati “Nimwishimishe by’igihe gito.”
  51,44,"Ariko bigometse ku itegeko rya Nyagasani wabo, maze bakubitwa n’ikibatsi cy’umuriro w’inkuba bareba"
  51,45,Ntibashoboraga guhaguruka (ngo bahunge) cyangwa ngo bitabare
  51,46,N’abantu ba Nuhu (ni uko twabagenje) mbere. Mu by’ukuri bari abantu b’ibyigomeke
  51,47,"Kandi ikirere twacyubakanye imbaraga, kandi mu by’ukuri nitwe tucyagura"
  51,48,N’isi twarayishashe; kandi ni twe dusasa neza
  51,49,"No muri buri kintu twaremyemo amoko abiri (ikigabo n’ikigore, iburyo n’ibumoso, hasi no hejuru,…) kugira ngo mwibuke (ubushobozi bwa Allah)"
  51,50,"Bityo, nimuhungire kwa Allah. Mu by’ukuri njye (Muhamadi) ndi umuburizi wanyu ugaragara umuturutseho"
  51,51,Kandi ntimuzabangikanye Allah n’ikigirwamana icyo ari cyo cyose. Mu by’ukuri njye (Muhamadi) ndi umuburizi wanyu ugaragara umuturutseho
  51,52,"Ni nk’uko, nta ntumwa n’imwe yageze ku babayeho mbere yabo ngo babure kuvuga bati “Ni umurozi cyangwa umusazi!”"
  51,53,"Ese (imvugo nk’izi) barazihererekanyaga? (Oya, si uko bimeze), ahubwo bose bari abantu barengera (imbibi za Allah)"
  51,54,Bityo (yewe Muhamadi) birengagize kandi ntuzabigayirwa (kuko wamaze gusohoza ubutumwa)
  51,55,Unibutse kuko mu by’ukuri urwibutso rugirira akamaro abemeramana
  51,56,Kandi nta kindi naremeye amajini n’abantu bitari ukugira ngo bangaragire
  51,57,"Simbakeneyeho amafunguro, ndetse nta n’ubwo mbakeneyeho ko bangaburira"
  51,58,"Mu by’ukuri Allah ni We Utanga amafunguro, Nyirimbaraga, Ukomeye bihebuje"
  51,59,"Kandi rwose abakora ibibi bazagira umugabane (w’ibihano) umeze nk’umugabane wa bagenzi babo (abababanjirije); bityo, bareke kunsaba kwihutisha (kubahana)"
  51,60,Ibihano bikomeye bizaba kuri ba bandi bahakanye bitewe n’umunsi basezeranyijwe
  52,1,Ndahiye Umusozi wa Twuur
  52,2,N’igitabo cyanditse (Qur’an)
  52,3,Ku mpapuro zikozwe mu ruhu (rusukuye) ruramburwa (kugira ngo gisomwe)
  52,4,N’ingoro (yo mu ijuru) ihora isurwa (n’abamalayika)
  52,5,N’igisenge gihanitse (ikirere)
  52,6,N’inyanja zibirinduye (ku munsi w’imperuka)
  52,7,Mu by’ukuri ibihano bya Nyagasani wawe bizabaho nta kabuza
  52,8,Ntagishobora kuzabikumira
  52,9,Umunsi ikirere kizatigita umutingito (ukomeye)
  52,10,N’imisozi ikagenda (nk’uko ibicu bigenda)
  52,11,Kuri uwo munsi ibihano bikomeye bizaba ku bahinyuye (ukuri)
  52,12,"Ba bandi bahugira mu kwishimisha mu biganiro byuzuye ibinyoma, bidafite akamaro"
  52,13,Umunsi bazasunikirwa mu muriro wa Jahanamu ku ngufu
  52,14,(Bazabwirwa bati) “Uyu ni wo muriro mwajyaga muhinyura.”
  52,15,Ese ibi (bihano mubona) ni uburozi cyangwa ntimubona
  52,16,"Ngaho nimuhiremo, kandi mwabyihanganira cyangwa mutabyihanganira, byose ni kimwe kuri mwe. Mu by’ukuri (ibyo muri kubona) ni ibihembo by’ibyo mwakoraga"
  52,17,Mu by’ukuri abagandukira (Allah) bazaba bari mu busitani n’inema (bihoraho)
  52,18,"Binezeza mu byo Nyagasani wabo yabahaye, ndetse no kuba Nyagasani wabo yabarinze ibihano by’umuriro"
  52,19,(Bazabwirwa bati) “Nimurye munanywe kandi mugubwe neza kubera ibyo mwajyaga mukora.”
  52,20,"Bazaba begamye ku bitanda bitondetse ku murongo. Tuzanabashyingira Huur ul-a’in (abagore bo mu Ijuru b’igikundiro, b’amaso manini)"
  52,21,"Naho ba bandi bemeye maze ababakomokaho bakabakurikira mu kwemera, tuzabahuza n’ababakomotseho (mu ijuru), kandi nta cyo tuzigera tugabanya mu bikorwa byabo. Buri muntu azabazwa ibyo yakoze"
  52,22,Tuzabaha imbuto n’inyama (by’amoko yose) bazajya bifuza
  52,23,Bazajya bahererekanyamo ibirahure by’ikinyobwa kitazabatera kuvuga amagambo adafite akamaro cyangwa ngo kibatere gukora ibyaha
  52,24,"Bazaba bazengurukwamo n’abahungu b’abahereza babo, bameze nk’inigi zishashagirana (Lu’ulu’u) zikiri mu bubiko bwazo"
  52,25,"Bamwe muri bo bazajya bahindukira barebe bagenzi babo, babazanya"
  52,26,Bavuga bati “Mbere (ku isi) twabaga turi mu miryango yacu dufite ubwoba n’impungenge (z’ibihano bya Allah)”
  52,27,"“None Allah yatugororeye, aturinda ibihano by’umuriro utwika.”"
  52,28,"Mu by’ukuri mbere twajyaga tumusenga (wenyine). Rwose ni We Mugiraneza, Nyirimbabazi"
  52,29,"Bityo, (yewe Muhamadi) komeza wibutse! Mu by’ukuri ku bw’ingabire za Nyagasani wawe (zo kuba warahawe ubutumwa), ntabwo uri umupfumu cyangwa umusazi (nk’uko babivuga)"
  52,30,"Ahubwo (abahakanyi) baravuga bati “(Muhamadi) ni umusizi, reka tumutege iminsi (azapfe nk’uko abandi basizi bapfuye)!”"
  52,31,"Babwire uti “Ngaho nimutegereze, mu by’ukuri ndi kumwe namwe mu bategereje.”"
  52,32,Cyangwa imitekerereze yabo ni yo ibategeka (kuvuga) ibyo? Cyangwa ahubwo ni abantu barengera (imbibi za Allah)
  52,33,"Ndetse bavuga ko (Qur’an) yayihimbiye? (Oya), ahubwo ntibemera"
  52,34,"Ngaho nibazane inkuru zimeze nk’iziyivugwamo (Qur’an), niba koko ari abanyakuri"
  52,35,"Ese (bibwira ko) baremwe nta cyo bakomowemo, cyangwa ni bo baremyi"
  52,36,Cyangwa bibwira ko baremye ibirere n’isi? Ahubwo ntibizera
  52,37,"Cyangwa bibwira ko bafite ibigega bya Nyagasani wawe? Cyangwa ni bo bagenga (b’isi, bakora ibyo bashaka)"
  52,38,Cyangwa bibwira ko bafite urwego buririraho (bajya mu ijuru) ngo bumvirize ibivugirwayo? Ngaho umwumviriza wabo nazane ibimenyetso simusiga
  52,39,"Cyangwa bibwira ko (Allah) afite abakobwa, mwe mukagira abahungu"
  52,40,"Cyangwa bibwira ko (wowe Muhamadi) ubasaba igihembo, none bakaba baremererwa n’ubwishyu"
  52,41,"Cyangwa bibwira ko bazi ibyihishe, bakaba babyandika (badakeneye ibyo ubabwira)"
  52,42,Cyangwa icyo bashaka ni ubugambanyi? Nyamara abahakanye ni bo bazahanirwa ubugambanyi bwabo
  52,43,Cyangwa bafite indi mana itari Allah? Ubutagatifu ni ubwa Allah kandi nta ho ahuriye n’ibyo bamubangikanya na byo
  52,44,"N’iyo baza kubona igice cy’ikirere kigwa hasi, bari kuvuga bati “Ni igicu gicucitse!”"
  52,45,"Bareke kugeza ubwo bazahura n’umunsi wabo, aho bazagwa igihumure bagapfa (kubera ibihano)"
  52,46,"Umunsi imigambi mibisha yabo itazagira icyo ibamarira, ndetse nta n’ubwo bazatabarwa"
  52,47,Kandi mu by’ukuri abakora ibibi bazahanishwa ibindi bihano (ku isi) mbere y’ibyo (ku munsi w’imperuka); ariko abenshi muri bo ntibabizi
  52,48,"Bityo (yewe Muhamadi), ihanganire itegeko rya Nyagasani wawe, kuko mu by’ukuri tuguhanzeho amaso. Ndetse unasingize ikuzo rya Nyagasani wawe igihe ubyutse (ugiye gusali)"
  52,49,"No mu ijoro ujye umusingiza, ndetse n’igihe urumuri rw’inyenyeri ruba rugenda rukendera"
  53,1,Ndahiye inyenyeri igihe irenga
  53,2,(Ko uyu) mugenzi wanyu (Intumwa Muhamadi) atigeze ayoba ndetse ko atigeze anateshuka (ku nzira y’ukuri)
  53,3,Nta n’ubwo avuga ashingiye ku marangamutima ye
  53,4,Ahubwo (ibyo avuga) ni ibyo ahishurirwa (na Allah)
  53,5,Yigishijwe (iyi Qur’an) n’umunyembaraga cyane (Malayika Jibrilu)
  53,6,"Ufite ububasha kandi utagira inenge, wagaragariye (Intumwa Muhamadi) mu ishusho ye y’ukuri"
  53,7,Ubwo (Malayika Jibrilu) yari mu kirere cyo hejuru
  53,8,"Nuko yegera (Intumwa Muhamadi), maze aramanuka akomeza kuyegera"
  53,9,(Yamwegereye) mu ntera ingana n’iri hagati y’amahembe abiri y’umuheto cyangwa bugufi kurushaho
  53,10,"Nuko (Allah) ahishurira umugaragu we (Muhamadi, abinyujije kuri Malayika Jibrilu) ibyo yagombaga kumuhishurira byose"
  53,11,Umutima (wa Muhamadi) ntiwigeze ubeshya ku byo wabonye
  53,12,None se muramugisha impaka ku byo yabonye (ubwo yazamukaga mu ijuru rya karindwi)
  53,13,Kandi rwose (Muhamadi) yaramubonye (Malayika Jibrilu) ubwo yamanukaga ku yindi nshuro
  53,14,Ubwo yari kuri Sidrat-il-Muntaha (Igiti cya nyuma)
  53,15,Ni na ho hari ubuturo bw’ijuru (ry’abemeramana)
  53,16,Ubwo icyo giti (Sidrat) cyatwikirwaga n’ibyagitwikiriye (urumuri rutangaje)
  53,17,"Indoro (y’Intumwa y’Imana) ntiyigeze itana, cyangwa ngo irengere (imbibi yari yashyiriweho)"
  53,18,Mu by’ukuri (Intumwa Muhamadi) yabonye bimwe mu bitangaza bihambaye bya Nyagasani wayo
  53,19,Ese ntimutekereza (ku bigirwamana musenga); Laata na Uza
  53,20,"Ndetse na Manaata, ikindi (kigirwamana) cya gatatu"
  53,21,Ese mwibwira ko mufite abana b’abahungu naho We (Allah) akagira ab’abakobwa
  53,22,Iryo ryaba ari igabana ribogamye
  53,23,"Ibyo (bigirwamana) nta kindi biri cyo usibye kuba ari amazina masa mwabihimbiye, mwe n’abakurambere banyu, Allah atigeze abahera uburenganzira. Rwose nta kindi bakurikira kitari ugukekeranya ndetse n’ibyo imitima (yabo) irarikira. Kandi mu by’ukuri bagezweho n’umuyoboro uturutse kwa Nyagasani wabo"
  53,24,Ese (mutekereza ko) umuntu yabona ibyo yifuza byose
  53,25,Allah ni We Mugenga w’ubuzima bw’imperuka n’ubw’isi
  53,26,"None se ni bangahe mu bamalayika bari mu birere, ubuvugizi bwabo butazigera bugira icyo bumara Allah atabanje kubitangira uburenganzira bikagirira akamaro uwo ashatse kandi yishimira"
  53,27,Mu by’ukuri abatemera imperuka bita abamalayika amazina y’igitsina gore
  53,28,"Kandi ibyo nta bumenyi babifitiye. Ndetse nta kindi bakurikira kitari ugukekeranya, kandi rwose ugukeka nta cyo kuvuze imbere y’ukuri"
  53,29,"Bityo, irengagize wa wundi wateye umugongo urwibutso rwacu nta kindi ashaka uretse ubuzima bw’isi"
  53,30,"(Ibyo bavuga) ni ho ubumenyi bwabo bugarukira. Mu by’ukuri Nyagasani wawe ni We uzi neza uwayobye inzira ye, kandi ni na We uzi neza abayobotse"
  53,31,"Kandi ibiri mu birere n’ibiri mu isi ni ibya Allah, (yashyizeho ayo mategeko) kugira ngo ahane inkozi z’ibibi kubera ibyo zakoze, ndetse anahembe ibyiza (ijuru) abakora ibyiza"
  53,32,"Ba bandi birinda ibyaha bikomeye n’ibikozasoni uretse kuba bagwa mu byaha byoroshye; mu by’ukuri imbabazi za Nyagasani wawe ziragutse. Ni We ubazi neza kuva yabarema abakuye mu gitaka, n’igihe mwari insoro muri nyababyeyi za ba nyoko. Bityo, ntimukigire abere kuko ari We uzi neza umugandukira"
  53,33,Ese (yewe Muhamadi) wabonye wa wundi wateye umugongo (akanga kumvira Allah)
  53,34,"Akanatanga bike (mu byo twamuhaye), nyuma akabireka burundu"
  53,35,Ese yaba afite ubumenyi bw’ibitagaragara akaba abona (ko ibyo intumwa Muhamadi yahishuriwe atari ukuri)
  53,36,Cyangwa ntiyabwiwe ibiri mu bitabo bya Musa
  53,37,Ndetse n’ibiri mu bya Ibrahimu wasohoje ubutumwa
  53,38,Ko nta we uzikorera umutwaro w’undi
  53,39,Kandi ko nta cyo umuntu azabona (ku munsi w’imperuka) usibye ibyo yashyizemo umuhate
  53,40,Kandi ko umuhate we uzagaragara (ku munsi w’imperuka)
  53,41,Maze akazabihemberwa ibihembo byuzuye
  53,42,Kandi ko iherezo (rya buri kintu) ari kwa Nyagasani wawe
  53,43,Kandi ko ari We (Allah) utera guseka (kwishima) no kurira (kubabara)
  53,44,No kuba ari We wisubiza ubuzima ndetse akanabutanga
  53,45,"No kuba ari we waremye ibitsina byombi, gabo na gore"
  53,46,Mu ntanga igihe zisohowe
  53,47,No kuba ari We uzarema bundi bushya (azura abapfuye)
  53,48,No kuba ari We utanga ubukungu akanatuma abantu bagira ibyo bigezaho
  53,49,No kuba ari We Nyagasani wa Shi’ira
  53,50,No kuba ari We woretse aba Adi bo hambere
  53,51,N’aba Thamudu ntiyagira uwo asigaza
  53,52,"Na mbere yabo, (yoretse) abantu ba Nuhu. Mu by’ukuri bari inkozi z’ibibi bakaba n’abarengera (amategeko ya Allah) bikabije"
  53,53,"Ndetse n’imidugudu (ya Sodoma) yabirinduwe, ni We wayibirinduye (ibyari hasi bijya hejuru n’ibyari hejuru bijya hasi)"
  53,54,Nuko (iyo midugudu) itwikirwa n’ibyayitwikiriye (ibihano bigizwe n’amabuye)
  53,55,None se (yewe muntu) ni izihe nema za Nyagasani wawe ushidikanyaho (ko atari ize)
  53,56,Uyu (Muhamadi) ni umwe mu (ruhererekane rw’) ababurizi bo hambere
  53,57,Umunsi w’imperuka uregereje
  53,58,Nta kindi cyawukumira usibye Allah (ushobora kuwihutisha cyangwa akawutinza)
  53,59,None se mutangajwe n’aya magambo (ya Qur’an)
  53,60,Mukaba museka (muyihakana) aho kurira
  53,61,Muhugiye mu bibarangaza
  53,62,"Bityo, nimwubamire Allah munamugaragire (wenyine)"
  54,1,Igihe cy’imperuka kiregereje ndetse n’ukwezi kwarasadutse
  54,2,"N’iyo (abahakanyi) babonye igitangaza, batera umugongo bakavuga bati “Ubu ni uburozi bugikomeje!”"
  54,3,"Barahakanye banakurikira irari ryabo, kandi buri kintu kizagira iherezo"
  54,4,Kandi rwose bagezweho n’inkuru zibabuza (gukora ibibi)
  54,5,"(Izo nkuru ziri muri Qur’an) zuje ubushishozi buhebuje, ariko uko kubaburira nta cyo kwabamariye"
  54,6,"Bityo (yewe Muhamadi), birengagize kandi (unabibutse) umunsi umuhamagazi azahamagarira kugana ku kintu kibi cyane (gucirwa urubanza ku munsi w’imperuka)"
  54,7,"Bazaba bubitse amaso (kubera ikimwaro), basohoka mu mva bameze nk’inzige zinyanyagiye"
  54,8,Bihuta bagana uhamagara. Abahakanyi bazavuga bati “Uyu ni umunsi ugoye.”
  54,9,"Na mbere yabo, abantu ba Nuhu bahinyuye umugaragu wacu, maze baravuga bati “Ni umusazi”, ndetse aranamaganwa"
  54,10,"Nuko asaba Nyagasani we (agira ati) “Rwose njye naneshejwe, ngaho tabara!”"
  54,11,"Nuko dufungura amarembo y’ikirere, hamanuka amazi yisuka ari menshi"
  54,12,"Nuko isi tuyikuramo amasoko, maze amazi (yo mu nsi no hejuru) arahura ku bw’itegeko ryagenwe"
  54,13,Maze (Nuhu) tumutwara mu gikozwe mu mbaho n’imisumari (inkuge)
  54,14,Cyagendaga (hejuru y’amazi) tugihanze amaso; (ibyo) biba igihembo cy’uwo bahakanye
  54,15,Rwose (iyi nkuru ya Nuhu) twarayiretse ngo ibe ikimenyetso (n’isomo ku bazaza nyuma ye). Ese hari uwibuka (ngo bimugirire akamaro)
  54,16,Mbega uko ibihano byanjye no kuburira kwanjye byari bimeze
  54,17,Kandi rwose Qur’an twarayoroheje kugira ngo ibe urwibutso. Ese hari uwibuka (ngo bimugirire akamaro)
  54,18,Aba Adi bahinyuye (Intumwa yabo Hudu); mbega uko ibihano byanjye no kuburira kwanjye byari bimeze
  54,19,Mu by’ukuri twaboherereje inkubi y’umuyaga uvuza ubuhuha ku munsi w’amakuba akomeye
  54,20,Uterura abantu bakamera nk’ingiga z’ibiti by’imitende byaranduwe
  54,21,Mbega uko ibihano byanjye no kuburira kwanjye byari bimeze
  54,22,Kandi rwose Qur’an twarayoroheje kugira ngo ibe urwibutso. Ese hari uwibuka (ngo bimugirire akamaro)
  54,23,Aba Thamudi bahinyuye kuburira (kwacu)
  54,24,Nuko baravuga bati “Ese ni gute twafata umuntu umwe unadukomokamo ngo tube ari we dukurikira? Rwose ubwo twaba turi mu buyobe n’ubusazi!”
  54,25,Ese ubu koko urwibutso ni we wenyine muri twe rwahawe? Ahubwo we ni umubeshyi akaba n’umwibone
  54,26,Bidatinze bazamenya umubeshyi w’umwibone uwo ari we
  54,27,Tugiye kuboherereza ingamiya (y’ingore) kugira ngo tubagerageze; bityo bagenzure unabihanganire
  54,28,Unababwire ko amazi bagomba kuyasangira na yo (ingamiya); buri wese azajya agira igihe cye cyo kuyanywaho
  54,29,Ariko bahamagaye mugenzi wabo (afata inkota) arayica
  54,30,Mbega uko ibihano byanjye no kuburira kwanjye byari bimeze
  54,31,"Mu by’ukuri twaboherereje urusaku rumwe gusa, maze bamera nk’ibyatsi byumye byaribaswe"
  54,32,Kandi rwose Qur’an twarayoroheje kugira ngo ibe urwibutso. Ese hari uwibuka (ngo bimugirire akamaro)
  54,33,Abantu ba Lutwi bahinyuye kuburira (kwacu)
  54,34,"Twaboherereje inkubi y’umuyaga uvanze n’amabuye (ubarimbura bose), usibye gusa umuryango wa Lutwi twarokoye mu rukerera"
  54,35,(Ibyo twabikoze) ku bw’ingabire ziduturutseho. Uko ni ko duhemba ushimira
  54,36,"Nyamara (Lutwi) yari yarababuriye ko bazahura n’ibihano byacu, nuko bashidikanya kuri uko kuburira (kwacu)"
  54,37,Baranamwinginze (ngo abahe) abashyitsi be (kugira ngo babakorere ubutinganyi). Nuko tubahuma amaso (tuvuga tuti) “Ngaho nimusogongere ibihano byanjye no kuburira (kwanjye)!”
  54,38,Kandi rwose twabazindukirije mu bihano bikomeza (kuzageza ku munsi w’imperuka)
  54,39,Ngaho nimusogongere ibihano byanjye no ku byo najyaga mbaburira
  54,40,Kandi rwose Qur’an twarayoroheje kugira ngo ibe urwibutso. Ese hari uwibuka (ngo bimugirire akamaro)
  54,41,Kandi rwose kuburira (kwanjye) kwageze ku bantu ba Farawo
  54,42,"Bahinyuye ibitangaza byacu byose, nuko turabafata tubahanisha ibihano by’Umunyacyubahiro bihebuje, Ushobora byose"
  54,43,"Ese abahakanyi banyu (b’i Maka) ni bo beza kurusha abo (abantu ba Adi, aba Thamudi, aba Nuhu n’aba Farawo, boretswe)? Cyangwa mufite ubudahangarwa bwanditse mu bitabo (bwo kutazahanwa)"
  54,44,"Cyangwa (abo bahakanyi) baravuga bati “Twe turi benshi dushyize hamwe, dushoboye kwitabara!”"
  54,45,Nyamara abo bishyize hamwe bazatsindwa banayabangire ingata
  54,46,"Ahubwo umunsi w’imperuka ni cyo gihe basezeranyijwe (cyo kuzahanirwaho), ndetse imperuka izaba iteye ubwoba cyane kandi irura"
  54,47,"Mu by’ ukuri, inkozi z’ibibi ziri mu buyobe (hano ku isi) kandi zizahanishwa umuriro utwika"
  54,48,Umunsi uburanga bwabo buzakururirwa mu muriro (bazabwirwa bati) “Ngaho nimwumve igihano cy’umuriro.”
  54,49,Mu by’ukuri buri kintu twakiremye ku rugero twagennye (igeno ryacyo)
  54,50,Kandi itegeko ryacu ni (ijambo) rimwe; (ryihuta) nko guhumbya no guhumbura
  54,51,Kandi rwose tworetse abantu bameze nkamwe (mu buhakanyi). Ese hari uwibuka (ngo bimugirire akamaro)
  54,52,Kandi buri kintu cyose bakoze cyandikwaga mu bitabo (by’ibikorwa byabo)
  54,53,"Na buri kintu, cyaba gito cyangwa kinini, kiranditse"
  54,54,Mu by’ukuri abagandukira Allah bazaba bari mu busitani n’imigezi (Ijuru)
  54,55,"Mu byicaro by’icyubahiro, hafi y’Umwami, Ushobora byose"
  55,1,Nyirimpuhwe (Allah)
  55,2,Yigishije (umuntu) Qur’an
  55,3,Yaremye umuntu
  55,4,Amwigisha gusobanura (mu buryo bwumvikana)
  55,5,Izuba n’ukwezi bigendera ku mubare (no kuri gahunda ya Allah)
  55,6,"N’ibyatsi birandaranda ndetse n’ibiti, byose birubama (bikicisha bugufi imbere ya Allah)"
  55,7,N’ikirere yagihanitse hejuru cyane (y’isi) ndetse ashyiraho n’ibipimo (bya buri kintu)
  55,8,Kugira ngo mutarengera mu bipimo (byagenwe)
  55,9,"Bityo, mujye mutanga ibipimo byuzuye kandi ntimukibishe iminzani"
  55,10,N’isi (Allah) yayishyiriyeho ibiremwa
  55,11,Irimo imbuto n’imitende ifite imbuto zitwikiriwe n’ibishishwa
  55,12,Ndetse n’impeke ziri mu bishishwa (byazo); iz’inyamisogwe n’izihumura
  55,13,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,14,(Allah) yaremye umuntu (Adamu) mu itaka ryumye ukomangaho rikirangira nk’ibikoresho bibumbye mu ibumba
  55,15,Anarema amajini mu birimi by’umuriro
  55,16,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,17,(Ni We) Nyagasani w’Uburasirazuba bubiri akaba na Nyagasani w’Uburengerazuba bubiri
  55,18,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,19,Yaretse inyanja ebyiri (ifite amazi y’urubogobogo n’indi y’urwunyunyu) zirahura
  55,20,Hagati yazo hari urubibi zitarenga (ruzitandukanya kugira ngo zitivanga)
  55,21,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,22,Muri zo havamo amasaro arabagirana (Lu-ulu-u) na Marijani
  55,23,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,24,"Kandi (Allah ni We) ufite ububasha ku mato manini agendera mu nyanja, ameze nk’imisozi"
  55,25,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,26,Buri ikiyiriho (isi) cyose kizapfa
  55,27,"Maze hasigare gusa uburanga butagatifu bwa Nyagasani wawe, Nyirikuzo n’icyubahiro"
  55,28,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,29,Buri cyaremwe cyose kiri mu birere no ku isi kiramusaba (ibyo cyifuza). Naho We buri munsi aba agena gahunda (z’ibiremwa)
  55,30,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,31,"Yemwe matsinda abiri (y’abantu n’amajini), tuzabacira imanza (ku munsi w’imperuka)"
  55,32,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,33,"Yemwe majini namwe bantu! Niba mufite ubushobozi bwo kugenda mukarenga imbago z’ibirere n’isi (muhunga ibihano bya Allah), muzagende. Ariko ntimushobora kuzirenga keretse ku bw’ububasha (bwa Allah)"
  55,34,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,35,"Muzohererezwa ikibatsi cy’umuriro n’umuringa (washongeshejwe), kandi ntimuzitabara"
  55,36,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,37,"(Mwibuke) ubwo ikirere kizasatagurika, maze kigahinduka nk’ururabo rutukura rumeze nk’amavuta yabize"
  55,38,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,39,"Kuri uwo munsi, nta muntu cyangwa ijini uzagira icyo abazwa ku bijyanye n’ibyaha bye (kuko bizaba bizwi neza)"
  55,40,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,41,"Inkozi z’ibibi zizamenyerwa ku bimenyetso byazo, kandi zizaterurwa zifatiwe mu bihorihori n’ibirenge byazo"
  55,42,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,43,Uyu ni umuriro wa Jahanamu inkozi z’ibibi zajyaga zihinyura
  55,44,"Bazaba bagenda bagaruka hagati yawo n’amazi yatuye, ashyushye cyane"
  55,45,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,46,"Ariko wa wundi utinya kuzahagarara imbere ya Nyagasani we, azaba afite ubusitani bubiri (mu Ijuru)"
  55,47,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,48,(Ubwo busitani buzaba burimo ibiti) bifite amashami acucitse kandi atoshye
  55,49,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,50,"Muri ubwo (busitani) bwombi, hazaba harimo amasoko abiri atemba"
  55,51,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,52,"Muri ubwo (busitani) bwombi, hazaba harimo ubwoko bubiri bwa buri rubuto"
  55,53,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,54,"Bazaba begamye ku bitanda bishasheho ihariri iremereye, kandi imbuto zo muri ubwo busitani zizaba zibari hafi"
  55,55,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,56,"(Ubwo busitani bwombi) buzaba burimo abagore bubika amaso yabo (kubera ikinyabupfura), batigeze bagira umuntu cyangwa ijini babakoraho kuva na mbere (bakiri amasugi)"
  55,57,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,58,(Bazaba bafite ubwiza) nk’ubw’amabuye y’agaciro ya Yaquut na Marjani
  55,59,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,60,Ese hari igihembo cy’ibyiza kitari ibyiza
  55,61,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,62,"Kandi uretse n’ubwo (busitani) bubiri, hari ubundi busitani bubiri"
  55,63,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,64,(Bufite) ibara ry’icyatsi cyijimye
  55,65,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,66,"Muri ubwo (busitani) bwombi, (naho) hazaba harimo amasoko abiri avubura amazi"
  55,67,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,68,"Muri ubwo (busitani) bwombi, hazaba harimo imbuto, imitende n’imikomamanga"
  55,69,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,70,Hazaba harimo abagore beza b’imico myiza
  55,71,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,72,Hazaba harimo abagore biyubashye bahora mu mahema
  55,73,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,74,"Mbere y’abo (bagabo bazaba bahawe), nta muntu cyangwa ijini wigeze ubakoraho"
  55,75,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,76,"(Abagabo babo) bazajya begama ku misego y’icyatsi, n’amagodora meza anepa atatse neza"
  55,77,None se (yemwe bantu namwe majini) ni iyihe mu ngabire za Nyagasani wanyu mwembi muhakana
  55,78,"Izina rya Nyagasani wawe, Nyirubuhambare n’icyubahiro, ryuje ubutungane n’imigisha"
  56,1,Ubwo imperuka izaba igeze
  56,2,Nta we uzashobora guhinyura ukuza kwayo
  56,3,"Izacisha bugufi (abazajya mu muriro), inashyire hejuru (abazajya mu ijuru)"
  56,4,Ubwo isi izatigiswa n’umutingito ukomeye
  56,5,N’imisozi igahindurwa ubuvungukira
  56,6,Maze ikaba umukungugu utumuka
  56,7,(Icyo gihe) muzaba muri mu byiciro bitatu
  56,8,Hari ab’iburyo; abo bantu b’iburyo ni bantu ki
  56,9,N’ab’ibumoso; abo bantu b’ibumoso ni bantu ki
  56,10,"N’aba mbere (ni ababimburiye abandi mu gukurikiza amategeko ya Allah bakiri ku isi), abo bazaba ari bo ba mbere (mu kwinjira mu Ijuru)"
  56,11,Abo ni bo bazaba bari hafi (ya Allah)
  56,12,Mu ijuru ryuje ingabire
  56,13,Abenshi (muri bo) bazaba ari itsinda rinini ryo mu bantu bo hambere (mbere y’Intumwa Muhamadi)
  56,14,Na bake mu bantu bo hanyuma (bakurikiye intumwa Muhamadi)
  56,15,Bazaba bari ku bitanda bitatswe na zahabu
  56,16,"Babyegamyeho, berekeranye"
  56,17,Bazaba bazengurukwamo n’abana b’abahungu bahoraho (badasaza cyangwa ngo bapfe)
  56,18,"(Bazaba babazengurutsamo) ibikombe, amabirika n’ibirahuri birimo ibinyobwa (byiza) byo mu masoko yo mu ijuru"
  56,19,Ntibizabatera kurwara umutwe ndetse nta n’ubwo bizabasindisha
  56,20,(Bazaba banazengurutswamo) imbuto bazihitiramo
  56,21,Ndetse n’inyama z’inyoni bazifuza
  56,22,Kandi (hazaba hari) ba Huur ul-a’in (abagore bo mu Ijuru b’igikundiro n’amaso manini)
  56,23,Bameze nk’inigi zishashagirana (Lu’ulu’u) zikiri mu bubiko bwazo
  56,24,Bizaba ari ibihembo by’ibyo bakoraga
  56,25,Muri ryo (Ijuru) nta magambo adafite akamaro cyangwa se ayatuma bakora ibyaha bazumvamo
  56,26,"Uretse (imvugo yo kuramukanya, igira iti) “Salamu, Salamu (amahoro, amahoro)!”"
  56,27,Naho ab’iburyo; ni bantu ki (mbega ibihembo by’abantu b’iburyo)
  56,28,Bazaba mu (ijuru ririmo) ibiti bya Sidiri bidafite amahwa
  56,29,N’insina zifite ibitoki by’amaseri agerekeranye
  56,30,No mu gicucu cyagutse (kandi gihoraho)
  56,31,N’amazi ahora atemba
  56,32,Ndetse n’imbuto nyinshi
  56,33,"Ntizizahundura (bitewe n’ihinduka ry’ibihe cyangwa ngo zigire igihe cyo kwera), kandi ntizizaba zibujijwe (kuri bo)"
  56,34,Bazaba banafite ibitanda biri hejuru
  56,35,Mu by’ukuri (abagore bo ku isi bazajya mu ijuru) tuzabarema bundi bushya
  56,36,Maze tubagire amasugi
  56,37,"Bakunda (abagabo babo gusa), kandi ari urungano"
  56,38,(Ibi byose) byateganyirijwe abantu b’iburyo
  56,39,Abenshi (muri bo) bazaba ari itsinda rinini ryo mu bantu bo hambere (mbere y’Intumwa Muhamadi)
  56,40,Na benshi mu bantu bo hanyuma (bakurikiye Intumwa Muhamadi)
  56,41,Naho abantu b’ibumoso; ni bantu ki (mbega ibihano by’abantu b’ibumoso)
  56,42,Bazaba bari mu muyaga utwika ndetse n’amazi yatuye
  56,43,No mu gicucu cy’umwotsi w’umukara
  56,44,(Icyo gicucu) nta mafu kizatanga ndetse nta n’icyiza kizagiturukaho
  56,45,Mu by’ukuri mbere bari babayeho mu buzima bwo kwinezeza (bigomeka kuri Allah)
  56,46,"Kandi bajyaga batsimbarara ku cyaha gihambaye (cyo kubangikanya Imana, ntibagire umugambi wo kubyicuza)"
  56,47,"Kandi bajyaga bavuga bati “ Ese nidupfa tugahinduka igitaka n’amagufa (akabora), tuzazurwa koko?”"
  56,48,“N’abakurambere bacu (bazazurwa) se?”
  56,49,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “(Yego) rwose, abo hambere n’abo hanyuma"
  56,50,"Bazakoranywa ku munsi uzwi, wagenwe (umunsi w’imperuka).”"
  56,51,Nuko mwe abayobye mukanahinyura ukuri
  56,52,Rwose muzarya ku giti cya Zaqumu
  56,53,Maze mucyuzuze inda
  56,54,Mukirenzeho amazi yatuye
  56,55,Muzayanywa nk’ingamiya zinywa zidashira inyota
  56,56,Iryo ni ryo zimano ryabo ku munsi w’ibihembo
  56,57,Ni twe twabaremye. None se kuki mutemera (izuka)
  56,58,Ese mutekereza iki ku byo musohora (amasohoro)
  56,59,Ese ni mwe muyarema cyangwa ni twe Muremyi
  56,60,Ni twe twabageneye urupfu kandi ntitwananirwa
  56,61,"Kubasimbuza abameze nkamwe, maze tukabaremamo (amashusho y’) ibindi mutazi"
  56,62,Kandi mu by’ukuri mwamenye ukuremwa (kwanyu) kwa mbere. None se kuki mutibuka
  56,63,Ese ntimubona ibyo muhinga
  56,64,"Ese ni mwe mubiha kumera no gukura, cyangwa ni twe tubikora"
  56,65,"Tubishatse twabigira ubushingwe, maze mugakomeza kumirwa"
  56,66,(Muvuga muti) “Rwose (twaruhiye ubusa none) dusigaye mu madeni”
  56,67,Cyangwa ahubwo turaburaniwe (tubuze byose)
  56,68,Ese ntimubona amazi munywa
  56,69,Ese ni mwe muyamanura mu bicu cyangwa ni twe tuyamanura
  56,70,"Iyo tuza kubishaka, twari kuyagira urwunyunyu (ntanyobwe). None se kuki mudashimira (Allah)"
  56,71,Ese ntimubona umuriro mucana
  56,72,Ese ni mwe mwaremye igiti cyawo (muwukomoramo) cyangwa ni twe Muremyi
  56,73,"Ni twe twawugize urwibutso (rw’umuriro wa Jahanamu), ndetse n’ingirakamaro ku bagenzi (n’abandi bose bawukeneye)"
  56,74,"Ngaho singiza izina rya Nyagasani wawe, Uhambaye"
  56,75,Ndahiye ibyimbo by’inyenyeri (mu isanzure)
  56,76,Kandi rwose iyo ni indahiro ihambaye iyo muza kumenya
  56,77,Ko mu by’ukuri (iyi) ari Qur’an Ntagatifu
  56,78,Iri mu gitabo kirinzwe neza (mu Ijuru)
  56,79,Kitajya kigira ugikoraho uretse abejejwe (bafite isuku)
  56,80,Ni uguhishurwa kwaturutse kwa Nyagasani w’ibiremwa
  56,81,Ese iyi nkuru (Qur’an) ni yo muhinyura
  56,82,"Aho (gushimira Allah) ku ngabire abaha, (mumwitura) kumuhakana"
  56,83,None se (kuki nta cyo mukora) igihe roho (y’umuntu ugiye gupfa) igeze mu muhogo
  56,84,Icyo gihe muba murebera
  56,85,"Kandi tuba turi hafi ye kubarusha, ariko mwe ntimubibona"
  56,86,"None se kuki, niba mwibwira ko nta cyo muzabazwa (mukaba mwibwira ko muri abanyembaraga)"
  56,87,"Mutayigarura (iyo roho mu mubiri wayo), niba koko muri abanyakuri"
  56,88,Niba (uwo muntu ugiye gupfa) ari mu ba hafi (ya Allah)
  56,89,"(Ateganyirijwe) umunezero n’impumuro y’ibyishimo, ndetse n’ubusitani bwuje ingabire (Ijuru)"
  56,90,(Uwo muntu ugiye gupfa) naba ari mu bantu b’iburyo
  56,91,(Azabwirwa ati) “Amahoro nabe kuri wowe kuko uri mu bantu b’iburyo.”
  56,92,"Ariko (uwo muntu ugiye gupfa) naba ari mu bahinyura (izuka), bayobye"
  56,93,Izimano rye rizaba ari amazi yatuye
  56,94,No kuzatwikirwa mu muriro
  56,95,Mu by’ukuri uku ni ko kuri kudashidikanywaho
  56,96,"Ngaho tagatifuza izina rya Nyagasani wawe, Uhambaye"
  57,1,"Ibiri mu birere n’ibiri ku isi bisingiza Allah, kandi ni We Nyiricyubahiro bihebuje, Nyirubugenge buhambaye"
  57,2,Ubwami bw’ibirere n’ubw’isi ni ubwe. Ni We utanga ubuzima n’urupfu. Kandi ni We ufite ubushobozi bwa buri kintu
  57,3,"Ni We Ntangiriro akaba n’Iherezo, Ugaragara (Uri hejuru ya buri kintu) akaba n’Utagaragara (uri bugufi ya buri kintu). Kandi ni We Mumenyi uhebuje wa buri kintu"
  57,4,"Ni We waremye ibirere n’isi mu minsi itandatu, hanyuma aganza hejuru ya Ar’shi. Azi ibyinjira mu butaka n’ibibusohokamo, ibimanuka mu kirere ndetse n’ibikizamukamo. Kandi aba ari kumwe namwe aho muri hose. Kandi Allah ni Ubona bihebuje ibyo mukora"
  57,5,Ubwami bw’ibirere n’isi ni ubwe. Kandi kwa Allah ni ho ibintu byose bisubizwa
  57,6,"Yinjiza ijoro mu manywa, akaninjiza amanywa mu ijoro. Kandi ni We Mumenyi uhebuje w’ibiri mu bituza (by’abantu)"
  57,7,"Nimwemere Allah n’Intumwa ye (Muhamadi), munatange mu byo yabaragije; kuko bamwe muri mwe bemeye bakanatanga (mu nzira ya Allah), bazagororerwa ibihembo bihebuje"
  57,8,None se kuki mutemera Allah kandi Intumwa ibahamagarira kwemera Nyagasani wanyu? Kandi (Allah) yaranakiriye isezerano ryanyu rikomeye; niba muri abemeramana nyakuri (ngaho nimwemere)
  57,9,"Ni We uhishurira umugaragu we (Muhamadi) amagambo asobanutse, kugira ngo abakure mu mwijima abaganisha ku rumuri. Rwose Allah ni Umunyempuhwe nyinshi kuri mwe, Umunyembabazi"
  57,10,"None se kuki mudatanga mu nzira ya Allah, kandi Allah ari We ufite izungura ry’ibirere n’isi? Abatanze bakanarwana mbere y’urugamba (rwo kubohora Maka) muri mwe, ntibahwanye (na ba bandi babikoze nyuma yaho); abo (babikoze mbere) bafite urwego rusumba urw’abatanze bakanarwana nyuma. Ariko bose Allah yabasezeranyije ibyiza. Kandi Allah azi bihebuje ibyo mukora"
  57,11,"Ni nde waguriza Allah inguzanyo nziza (atanga amaturo n’ibindi bikorwa by’ubugiraneza), ngo (Allah azayimwishyure) amukubiye inshuro nyinshi, ndetse azanamugororere ibihembo bihebuje"
  57,12,"Umunsi uzabona abemeramana n’abemeramanakazi urumuri rwabo rukataje imbere n’iburyo bwabo (babwirwa) bati “Dore inkuru nziza yanyu uyu munsi! Ni ubusitani butembamo imigezi (Ijuru), muzabamo ubuziraherezo. Iyi ni yo ntsinzi ihambaye.”"
  57,13,"Umunsi indyarya z’abagabo n’iz’abagore zizabwira abemeramana ziti “Nimudutegereze turahure ku rumuri rwanyu!” Zizabwirwa ziti “Nimusubire inyuma (ku isi) mushake urumuri!” Maze hagati yabo hashyirwe urukuta rufite umuryango. Imbere yarwo hari impuhwe, naho hanze yarwo hakaba ibihano"
  57,14,"(Indyarya) zizabahamagara (abemeramana) zibabwira ziti “Ese ntitwari kumwe namwe (ku isi)?” Bazisubize bati “Yego! Ariko mwishyize mu bigeragezo, mutega iminsi (Intumwa n’abemeramana), munishyira mu gushidikanya kandi munashukwa n’irari ryanyu kugeza ubwo itegeko rya Allah (urupfu) risohoye. Nuko umushukanyi (Shitani) abatesha umurongo wa Allah.”"
  57,15,Uyu munsi nta ncungu yanyu (mwe ndyarya) cyangwa iy’abahakanye iri bwakirwe. Ubuturo bwanyu ni mu muriro. Ni wo muzabana kandi ni na wo herezo ribi
  57,16,"Ese igihe nticyari cyagera ngo imitima y’abemeye yicishe bugufi kubera kwibuka Allah n’ibyahishuwe by’ukuri (Qur’an)? No kugira ngo ntibabe nk’abahawe igitabo mbere yabo, nuko igihe (cyo gutegereza ibyo Intumwa zabasezeranyije) kikababana kirekire, maze imitima yabo ikinangira; kandi abenshi muri bo bari ibyigomeke"
  57,17,Mumenye ko Allah aha isi ubuzima nyuma yo gupfa kwayo (gukakara). Mu by’ukuri twabasobanuriye ibimenyetso kugira ngo mutekereze
  57,18,"Mu by’ukuri ba bandi batanga amaturo b’abagabo n’abagore, bakanaguriza Allah inguzanyo nziza, (Allah azabishyura) abakubiye inshuro nyinshi, ndetse azanabagororera ibihembo bihebuje"
  57,19,"Na ba bandi bemeye Allah n’intumwa ze (nta n’imwe barobanuye), ni bo banyakuri ndetse bakaba n’abahamya kwa Nyagasani wabo. Bazagororerwa ibihembo byabo n’urumuri rwabo. Naho abahakanye bakanahinyura amagambo yacu, bazaba abo mu muriro"
  57,20,"Mumenye ko ubuzima bw’isi nta kindi buri cyo uretse kuba ari umukino, kwinezeza, imitako, kwiyemera hagati yanyu ndetse no kwiratana imitungo n’abana. (Ibyo bigereranywa) nk’ibimera bishimisha abahinzi nyuma yo kubona imvura, hanyuma bikuma ukabona bibaye umuhondo; nuko (byamara kumagara) bigahinduka utuvungukira. Ariko ku munsi w’imperuka hazaba ibihano bikomeye (ku bahakanyi), ndetse n’imbabazi no kwishimirwa na Allah (ku bemeramana). Kandi ubuzima bw’isi nta cyo buri cyo uretse kuba ari umunezero ushukana"
  57,21,"Nimwihutire gushaka imbabazi ziva kwa Nyagasani wanyu, n’ijuru rifite ubugari bungana n’ubw’ikirere n’isi; ryateguriwe abemeye Allah n’intumwa ze. Izo ni ingabire za Allah aha uwo ashaka; kandi Allah ni Nyiringabire zihambaye"
  57,22,Nta kibi cyagera ku isi cyangwa ngo kibabeho kitanditse mu gitabo (kirinzwe) mbere y’uko tukibeshaho. Mu by’ukuri ibyo kuri Allah biroroshye
  57,23,"Kugira ngo mutababazwa n’ibyabacitse cyangwa ngo mwiratane ibyo mwahawe. Mu by’ukuri Allah ntakunda umwirasi wese, w’umwibone"
  57,24,"Ba bandi bagira ubugugu bakanabushishikariza abantu. Ariko uzatera umugongo (kumvira Allah, amenye ko) Allah ari Uwihagije, Usingizwa cyane"
  57,25,"Rwose twohereje intumwa zacu tuzihaye ibimenyetso bigaragara n’ibitangaza, ndetse tunazihishurira ibitabo n’ubutabera, kugira ngo abantu bimakaze ubutabera. Twanamanuye icyuma cy’ubutare gifite imbaraga zihambaye kandi kinafitiye abantu akamaro. (Ibyo byose byakozwe) kugira ngo Allah yerekane abamutabara (abatabara idini rye) ndetse n’Intumwa ze kandi batamuzi. Mu by’ukuri Allah ni Umunyacyubahiro bihebuje, Utsinda"
  57,26,"Kandi rwose twohereje Nuhu na Ibrahimu, maze duha urubyaro rwabo ubuhanuzi n’ibitabo. Muri bo hari abayobotse ariko abenshi muri bo babaye ibyigomeke"
  57,27,"Hanyuma tubakurikiza (izindi) ntumwa zacu zaje zitera ikirenge mu cyabo. Twakurikijeho kohereza Issa mwene Mariyamu, tumuha Ivanjili, tunashyira ubuntu n’impuhwe mu mitima y’abamukurikiye, ariko bihimbiye kwiyegurira Imana (banga gushaka cyangwa gushakwa) nyamara nta byo twabategetse, (twabategetse) gusa gushaka ishimwe rya Allah, gusa ntibabyubahirije nk’uko bikwiye. Bityo, abemeye muri bo twabahaye ibihembo bakwiye, nyamara abenshi muri bo bari ibyigomeke"
  57,28,"Yemwe abemeye (Intumwa Musa na Issa)! Nimugandukire Allah kandi munemere Intumwa ye (Muhamadi)! (Allah) azabaha impuhwe ze zikubye kabiri, anabahe urumuri mugendana ndetse anabababarire ibyaha byanyu. Allah ni Ubabarira bihebuje, Nyirimbabazi"
  57,29,"(Ibyo byose abikora) kugira ngo abahawe ibitabo bamenye ko nta bushobozi ubwo ari bwo bwose bagira mu ngabire za Allah, kandi ko ingabire zose ziri mu biganza bya Allah, akaba aziha uwo ashaka. Kandi Allah ni Nyiringabire zihambaye"